2層目までが残されている。[ref]画像:<a href=\"http://fedorareport.com/2011/04/11/third-generation-iraqi-looks-after-abrahams-birthplace/\">Third-generation Iraqi looks after Abraham’s birthplace | The Fedora Report</a>[/ref]</p>\n<p>[space size=\"\" line=\"yes\" style=\"solid\"]</p>\n<h3>シュメールの各主要都市国家の遺跡場所</h3>\n<p>[put_wpgm id=8]</p>\n", "B.C.4000 メソポタミア シュメール都市国家成立", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "2729-autosave-v1", "", "", "2015-07-15 22:10:29", "2015-07-15 13:10:29", "", "2729", "http://vccw.dev/uncategorized/2729-autosave-v1", "0", "revision", "", "0");
